title.Name: title
title.Value: Action Board Sports Reviews the Arbor Backlash Longboard Skateboard

description.Name: description
description.Value:
The Backlash is definitely the most shradical option in Arbor's Icon Downhill Series. It may just look like a brick but if you look closer you'll see a rockered platform and a full functional kicktail and nose. A 24″ wheelbase isn't the best for big mountain bombs but for most downhill, freeride, and urban mayhem, you'll be happy you have a smaller wheelbase and a kicktail for some serious ripping. And with an 8 ply construction it's not so hard to muscle ollies. Stoked on this one!

http://absboards.com/?s=backlash&post_type=product

Dimensions:

Length: 39.75″

Width: 9.75″

Wheelbase: 24.00″

Construction: 8 Plys of Sustainable Maple with a Sustainable Koa Veneer Basesheet

Artist: Eric Waetzig
